    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification defines a method for a protected resource to query an OAuth 2.0 authorization server to determine the active state of an OAuth 2.0 token and to determine meta-information about this token.  OAuth 2.0 deployments can use this method to convey information about the authorization context of the token from the authorization server to the protected resource.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
